com.facebook.buck.cxx.toolchain.nativelink

Interface NativeLinkable

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AbstractCxxLibrary
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CxxLibrary, CxxPrecompiledHeaderTemplate, CxxPrefixHeader, DLibrary, HalideLibrary, HaskellLibrary, PrebuiltAppleFramework, PrebuiltCxxLibrary, PrebuiltHaskellLibrary, PreInclude, RustLibrary, SwiftRuntimeNativeLinkable, SystemLuaCxxLibrary

    public interface NativeLinkable
    Interface for BuildRule objects (e.g. C++ libraries) which can contribute to the top-level link of a native binary (e.g. C++ binary).
